    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for throughout its ownership. The exterior maintains a strong shine, though you may find a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with the upholstery and dashboard showing very little wear. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. It offers a great balance of reliability and aesthetic appeal without the premium price of a showroom-new car.",
