    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a remarkable opportunity to own a vehicle that perfectly balances proven reliability with exceptional value. This unit has been meticulously vetted through our multi-point inspection process, ensuring it meets our rigorous standards for safety and performance. Boasting a clean history and a well-preserved interior, it offers a refined driving experience that rivals much newer models. For the buyer who demands quality and transparency, this vehicle stands as a testament to conscientious ownership and is fully prepared for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34900.0,
