    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m finally parting ways with my absolute favorite ride. She\u2019s been such a joy to own\u2014reliable, smooth, and honestly, a real head-turner on our streets. I\u2019ve taken great care of her, and while she\u2019s got a couple of tiny beauty marks from our adventures together, they just add character to an otherwise fantastic machine. She\u2019s got plenty of miles and smiles left to give. I\u2019d love for her to go to someone who will appreciate her as much as I have. Swing by for a coffee and a test drive!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
