      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This chassis remains remarkably stiff, offering surgical turn-in and a linear powerband that pulls hard to redline. I\u2019ve personally verified the compression across all cylinders and refreshed the cooling system with a high-flow water pump and aluminum radiator to ensure thermal stability under load. The suspension geometry is dialed in with upgraded bushings, eliminating the typical deflection found in high-mileage examples. It\u2019s a driver-focused machine with crisp synchros and a limited-slip diff that still locks up tight. This isn't your average neglected daily; it\u2019s a mechanically sorted athlete ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 38500.0,
